# Exploration: stat

## Rounds
  round 0: 111 isolated cumulative, 17 identical in round (single-phase)

## Observed: 7/7 flags
  4 solo, 3 via combination
  1 behavioral aliases detected
  robustness: 10 robust, 0 moderate, 0 fragile

Aliases: -L = --dereference, -f = --file-system, -t = --terse

